INIT=$(node ~/.claude/get-shit-done/bin/gsd-tools.cjs init todos)
```

Extract from init JSON: `commit_docs`, `date`, `timestamp`, `todo_count`, `todos`, `pending_dir`, `todos_dir_exists`.

